    <a class="article-thumb-wrap" href="/the-interpreter/israel-hamas-conflict-key-questions-long-difficult-war">
      <div class="article-thumb"
           style="background-image: url('https://www.lowyinstitute.org/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/2023-10/GettyImages-1713633258.jpg?itok=tL1QryJg'">
       </div>
    </a>

    <div class="article-title">
      <h3>
        <a href="/the-interpreter/israel-hamas-conflict-key-questions-long-difficult-war">
          Israel-Hamas conflict: Key questions for a “long and difficult war”
        </a>
      </h3>
    </div>

    <div class="pv-sm">
      <div class="article-precede">
        The latest fighting is quickly being incorporated by other nations to advance their own goals.
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
